Class groupparty

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    geniusweb.connection.Connectable<geniusweb.inform.Inform,geniusweb.actions.Action>, geniusweb.party.Party, tudelft.utilities.listener.Listener<geniusweb.inform.Inform>

    public class groupparty
extends geniusweb.party.DefaultParty
    A simple party that places random bids and accepts when it receives an offer with sufficient utility.

    parameters

    parameters
    minPower This value is used as minPower for placed Votes. Default value is 2.
    maxPower This value is used as maxPower for placed Votes. Default value is infinity.
